repertoire of regional concerns. Other high- level groups deal with technical aspects of governance or with human rights. Some examples of CSO action are: Concerned citizens in the Philippines. The Concerned Citizens of Abra Good Govern- ment (CCAGG) is an NGO that monitors government projects in the Abra region of the northern Philippines with the support of UNDP.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "faf924d6-dd00-44ba-b2c8-a2353b7b9b89": {"__data__": {"id_": "faf924d6-dd00-44ba-b2c8-a2353b7b9b89", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-report-2008-tackling-corruption-transforming-lives", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Asia-Pacific Human Development Report 2008: Tackling Corruption, Transforming Lives", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-report-2008-tackling-corruption-transforming-lives", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "0876a77a3616a9dfcffd216b6d6ad6fc7a5edce1191c501edd661245880a7060"}, "2": {"node_id": "0a4a48d9-16d6-405d-9bd8-f8cb718a7424", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-report-2008-tackling-corruption-transforming-lives", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "0f18ceeb8eac761186b1ae24a03a92a550eef14418c5726c575e8366dc7f59b9"}}, "hash": "1f51b576c4092b255a72c30d2357316d728c3d3